 <text>
  <front>
   <head>Moral SONG.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="quatrain">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">WOuld we attain the happiest State,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">That is design'd us here;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No Joy a Rapture must create,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">No Grief beget Despair.</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No Injury fierce Anger raise,</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">No Honour tempt to Pride;</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No vain Desires of empty Praise</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Must in the Soul abide.</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">No Charms of Youth, or Beauty move</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">The constant, settl'd Breast:</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">Who leaves a Passage free to Love,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Shall let in, all the rest.</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">In such a Heart soft Peace will live,</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Where none of these abound;</l>
     <l n="15" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="8">The greatest Blessing, Heav'n do's give,</l>
     <l n="16" met="-+|-+|-+" line_length="6">Or can on Earth be found.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
